Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"October 21, 1600"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Around 2:00 p.m."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sekigahara"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with Shimazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oorah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:36.13,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fukushima Masanori--Eastern Army Commander"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget Ukita and Ishida--\Nthe entire Western Army is routed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this final moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why don't you surrender, Shimazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't mess with...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Shimazu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to inform you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Fukushima was unable\Nto withstand Shimazu's fierce attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you assist us with pursuit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.01,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ii Naomasa\NGeneral of the Eastern Army"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 1\NFight Song"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Utouzaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lives for the commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Toyohisa!\N--Please withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle! Please withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:16.32,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shimazu Yoshihiro--Western Army General"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're returning \Nto Satsuma, too, Toyohisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do want to go back. If I'm to die,\NI want to die in Satsuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I and all these troops die here,\Nas long as you return to Satsuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this battle is a victory for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rearguard! Form up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemy is Ii Naomasa's Red Devils,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the greatest foe that Tokugawa has mustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A truly worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to give our lives... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let them go back to Sasshuu alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be a shame on \Nthe Ii Clan of Tokugawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stall for time! Hold up the\Nenemy as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold back as many as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you, Toyohisa!\NI'll be waiting in Satsuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting! You are not\Nallowed to die, Toyohisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lucky guy, to have an old man like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now! It's time to do a warrior's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear not! Run them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That was splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Toyohisa of the Shimazu \NClan, undersecretary
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Imperial Minister of the Center!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Naomasa of the Ii Clan,\Nundersecretary to the Ministry of War!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know you've been defeated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall have your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh... what are you\Ntalking about, you old fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head won't be yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Naomasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defend our lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the idiot, Naomasa,\Nthe Chamberlain of the Ii Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--My lord!\N--My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Naomasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw! Withdraw now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Naomasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your head here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your head with me! Naomasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to Satsuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Out for lunch\NBe back in a while"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please take a number"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle of Sekigahara is over"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shimazu Toyohisa"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Out for lunch\NBe back in a while"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?! Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...! I am going back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to Satsuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shimazu Toyohisa"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to it, brother? Did it die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! It's covered with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you. Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is "earless," brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devils. I must've been \Nsent to hell after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't an ordinary dying man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This language...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Drifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:11:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to take him to that deserted castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sooo heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.88,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Drag drag drag..." "Drip drip"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must weigh a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the lord ever finds out\Nabout this, we'll be damned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get any closer to \Nthe castle, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if you scream, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing is one of you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a lot for us to bring it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down. I don't understand. And speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't speak slower, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a Drifter like you? Look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't understand them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get killed if they find out\Nwe not only entered the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also met with a Drifter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry and get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is a warrior. Could he be\Nfrom the Land of the Rising Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers brought a dying man.\NHe is from the Land of the Rising Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a warrior of some clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is barely breathing, but he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have proper medication,\Nbut tend to his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His strength and fate may keep him alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How intriguing life is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyohisa! Toyohisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was your first battle, yet you've\Nbrought back an enemy's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job! What a fine boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Father!\N--Toyohisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've just been stitched up.\NYou'll die if you move around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me who I am? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! Who are you\Nand where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mokkou Crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a member of the Oda Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A member?! Don't be so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Oda and the Oda is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Nobunaga... the former\NMinister of the Right of the Oda Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous, you stupid fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the fool. You \Ncall yourself Nobunaga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Nobunaga has been dead for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means this must be the next world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you are impersonating Nobunaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a devil from hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:03.70,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Quack quack quack"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please pluck feathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time on your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pluck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pluck pluck pluck"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said Nobunaga had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People really do think I died then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He died!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was betrayed and killed by Akechi's\Nforces at Honnouji Temple in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a full eighteen years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! Eighteen years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been even a half year\Nsince the baldy assaulted Honnouji
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was thrown into this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've been telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are either a devil from hell or a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, you are just a madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help laughing,\Nseeing you two making a big fuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...over something as insignificant\Nas ten or fifteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him. Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:33.61,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nasu Suketaka Yoichi"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nasu Suketaka Yoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rumble rumble rumble"\NYou are from the time of the Genpei War.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:40.08,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rumble rumble rumble"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was over 400 years ago!\NThat's too absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you believe it\Nabsurd or not, I am who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be dreaming!\NWithout a doubt, this is a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who are you and where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Shimazu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyohisa of the Shimazu Clan!\NI am the son of Shimazu Iehisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:13.99,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shimazu" "Big City"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where? Where? Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! It's in the far edge of Kyushu...\NA super hick town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that clan. A Lord Shimazu\Nlived in my time as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my memory is correct, he was from\Nsomewhere in the countryside of Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Your family must have\Nbeen provincial for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move around too much, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For I've just stitched up your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a resilient man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called yourself "Nobunaga," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you die at the Honnouji Temple?\NYou're supposed to be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I would allow myself\Nto be killed by that baldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took Ranmaru with me and ran around,\Ntrying to escape the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way in hell you'll kill me, you old fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to betrayals like yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I found myself in an unfamiliar place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, I saw a strange stone passage\Nfilled with countless doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the passage\Nwas a mysterious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here. I met him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also met the man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while I was withdrawing from\Nthe Great Battle at Sekigahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekigahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it in Mino?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was a great battle between\NTokugawa's forces and Ishida's forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, as in that little toady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why on earth did Tokugawa \Nhave to fight such a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, after the death of the regent,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the country slid back into civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regent?! Why the hell was\Nthe regent running the state?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the regent gained control of\Nthe whole country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regent Hideyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me how the hell\Nthat bald rat took over the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! Don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hideyoshi's the one who defeated \NAkechi, destroyed Shibata,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then conquered the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did Katsuie die?! How about Oichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't know!\N--Niwa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumasu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshiie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nobodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Oda are now just minions of Ieyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody remembers the clan's sovereignty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Nobutada?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what happened to my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died! His Nijou Palace\Nwas attacked by Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thought you were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fought to the bitter end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son was stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot... Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should have gotten out\Nof there as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fifty years of human life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I did for those\Nfifty years of my life was in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also surprised to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Lord Nobunaga that the \NMinamoto Clan was overthrown,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Kamakura Shogunate\Nwas destroyed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me you were Nobunaga, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw this man, I thought\Nhe was the famous Mori Ranmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that would've been true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they are talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this far distance, it's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semu, respond to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going? Did you catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. They are certainly Drifters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of them are gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Octobrist"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to do something about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it will be the end of the world for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Smell of Battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Elven Village under Siege"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 2\NFootsteps"
